  <brief_title>A Comparison of Clinical Simulation and Classical Learning for Airway Management in Medical Students</brief_title>
  <official_title>Title: A Comparison of Clinical Simulation and Classical Learning for Airway Management in Medical Students: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
